Prompt for LinkedIn Networking Automation
Objective: Identify and connect with Recruiters or Senior Engineers at specific high-paying product companies for fresher SDE/GTE roles.

1. Target Companies: Providence, Chargebee, Walmart, Cognizant, Groww, Innovaccer, Razorpay, PhonePe, Postman, BrowserStack, Zepto, Swiggy, Zomato, SAP, Cisco, Oracle, Publicis Sapient.

2. Search & Filter Criteria:

Job Titles to Search: "Graduate Trainee Engineer", "Associate Software Engineer", "SDE 1", "Backend Developer".
People to Target:
Search for:OROR.
Location Filter: MUST be in Hyderabad, Bangalore, or Chennai.
Verification: Before sending, double-check that their current profile states they are employed at one of the target companies and reside in one of the 3 cities.
3. Execution Steps:

Search for a target company + "Recruiter" or "Senior Engineer".
Apply the location filter (Bangalore/Hyderabad/Chennai).
Click "Connect" -> "Add a Note".
Select the appropriate template below and replaceand.
4. Connection Templates:

Template 1: Recruiter (If they have a fresher opening) "Hi [Name], I'm Alisha — final-year CS student (9.85 CGPA), interning at Darwinbox building backend systems with Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB & LLM pipelines (Groq API). 600+ DSA solved. I noticed a fresher opening at [Company] and would love to connect — happy to discuss how my background makes me a good fit for the role!"
Template 2: Recruiter (General/No specific opening) "Hi [Name], I'm Alisha — final-year CS student (9.85 CGPA), interning at Darwinbox building backend systems with Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB & LLM pipelines (Groq API). 600+ DSA solved. Would love to connect — happy to know if there are any upcoming fresher openings where I could be a good fit at [Company]!"
Template 3: Senior Employee (If company has opening) "Hi [Name], I'm Alisha — final-year CS student (9.85 CGPA), interning at Darwinbox building backend systems with Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB & LLM pipelines (Groq API). 600+ DSA solved. I noticed an opening at [Company] and would love to connect — also happy to hear your perspective on the team culture and tech stack!"
Template 4: Senior Employee (General networking) "Hi [Name], I'm Alisha — final-year CS student (9.85 CGPA), interning at Darwinbox building backend systems with Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB & LLM pipelines (Groq API). 600+ DSA solved. I'm a fan of your work at [Company] and would love to connect — happy to learn about your journey and the engineering standards there!"
